      <step id="step_20D77818EEC34C5B9997ABC1ECC9082E">
        <cmd>To delete an idea, click the arrow next to the idea title and
			 click 
			 <uicontrol>Delete</uicontrol>, then click 
			 <uicontrol>Delete</uicontrol> when prompted to confirm the deletion. 
